{"tid":2043293,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"胡錫進: 香港勢必報復 吃虧的是美方","createTime":"2020-05-30T10:19:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T15:33:45.000Z","uid":240362,"like":29,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"87643a0a8c4beb8c254fdd8e88df9fab82c99063","tid":2043293,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T10:19:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529310-20200530.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529310-20200530.htm&d=qJ6fIGaH6M%2FMetNSomypD6nyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=05ccd881\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529310-20200530.htm&h=93158df1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529310-20200530.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1529310_1_L_20200530172559.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1529310_1_L_20200530172559.jpg&h=de407671&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地《環球時報》總編輯胡錫進下午在微博再發表長文，認為包括香港在內的整個中國，不用怕美國總統特朗普宣布的制裁。<br />\n<br />\n胡錫進認為，香港對美國出口有限，大部分是美國對香港出口，一年300多億美元順差，華盛頓如果把香港關稅與中國內地看齊，香港勢必報復，吃虧的是美方。無論美國對香港直接出口還是轉口貿易都將遭到打擊，會對特朗普競逐連任的選情造成嚴重威脅。"},{"pid":"4c7d3bee85165ddb1b11d58a2a353410aff7e9d0","tid":2043293,"uid":359022,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T10:21:16.000Z","msg":"垃圾環時<br />\n咁快入主<br />\n幾時輪到你代表香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n機場果次未死夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63a2deae990e7f82e82db48c1b7799f613a99f60","tid":2043293,"uid":21470,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T10:21